title: Soho Incident (a.k.a. Spin A Dark Web In USA) [1956] Faith Domergue, Lee Patterson

sources.title: Soho Incident (a.k.a. Spin A Dark Web In USA) [1956] Faith Domergue, Lee Patterson
sources.description: Soho Incident , released in the United States as Spin a Dark Web , is a 1956 British FILM NOlR directed by Vernon Sewell and starring Faith Domergue and Lee Patterson. The screenplay is based on Wide Boys Never Work, a novel by Robert Westerby.   You can find out more about this movie from Wikipedia and there is also a review from the movie blog  D for Doom .
